#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Account password"</h2>
To use this software, you must login to the Brightsands software suite.
In most cases, you will be given an account and password (and privileges)
on this system by the software administrator, but in some cases you create
the account yourself.
<p>Type in the password of the account you are using or the new password of the
account you wish to create.  There really are no restrictions on your password,
but if you are creating an account, you'll need to be able to type it twice.
